{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She would not-- there were times when I wouldn't see her more than maybe once a month or so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She would be away a lot, on the road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I didn't know what to do with those.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was accumulating them, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was afraid to spread them out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was afraid to take them home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I wouldn't want to  keep them at home, because we had a German family living with us, sharing the same apartment, a couple with a little 10-year-old boy, and-- the [?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Terushkas ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I really had a dilemma.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually, I found a way to deal with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the darkroom, there were two loose boards in the floor, on the right, directly underneath the tank, the-- the chemical tank.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was rotting, that floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, maybe I'll find a metal box and keep them there, which I did for a while.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then I was afraid that it may leak, the chemicals may leak into it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had such-- such problems, one after another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could not simply accumulate those pictures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wanted to get them out as fast as I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One day, I didn't see Alexandra for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I decided to drop those pictures off to her sister, Joanna's house, which was a few blocks from the studio.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were all involved in the underground, the resistance, sister, her brother-in-law, her brother, Lech, who was supposed to, at some point, rescue me from the other studio, which-- it failed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one day, I remember, I came, with-- in the middle of the day, without my armband.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was already the ghetto time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were not allowed to move by yourself in the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took off the armband.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
